00:27:41.616 --> 00:27:42.950
Kaj?

00:27:46.495 --> 00:27:48.372
Hecaš se, ne?

00:27:49.415 --> 00:27:51.918
Sasha, hecaš se, ne?

00:27:55.546 --> 00:27:56.923
Kaj?

00:28:00.551 --> 00:28:02.261
Kaj, hudiča, je to?

00:28:10.603 --> 00:28:12.146
<i>Daj!</i>

00:28:13.272 --> 00:28:14.899
<i>Poskusi!</i>

00:28:16.275 --> 00:28:18.652
<i>Saj se trudim.</i>

00:28:26.944 --> 00:28:28.671
<i>Pa tole?</i>

00:29:35.438 --> 00:29:37.940
Kaj počneš?

00:29:38.541 --> 00:29:41.141
Slišiš?

00:29:43.785 --> 00:29:45.829
Kaj, hudiča, je to?

00:30:04.486 --> 00:30:05.946
Si pripravljena?

00:30:38.032 --> 00:30:40.576
Hvala, da si bil sinoči
prijazen z mano.

00:30:41.452 --> 00:30:44.330
Tisto je bilo noro.
–Ja, res je.

00:30:44.580 --> 00:30:47.041
Vsekakor.
–Greš noter?

00:30:47.333 --> 00:30:49.293
Cimrinega avta ni.

00:30:53.255 --> 00:30:55.132
Lahko znova poskusiva.

00:30:56.634 --> 00:30:58.636
Te stvari se dogajajo.

00:30:59.386 --> 00:31:01.972
Pravzaprav ne.

00:31:02.306 --> 00:31:04.141
Meni ne.

00:31:07.603 --> 00:31:09.730
Dejansko tudi meni ne.

00:31:11.398 --> 00:31:15.069
Ni se mi še zgodilo,
da tipu ne bi prišlo.

00:31:16.570 --> 00:31:18.030
Pridi.

00:31:20.074 --> 00:31:21.992
Lačna sem.

00:31:22.201 --> 00:31:23.619
Kristus.

00:31:27.039 --> 00:31:28.374
Kaj je?

00:31:30.209 --> 00:31:31.669
Nič.

00:31:32.002 --> 00:31:33.420
Nič ni.

00:31:33.587 --> 00:31:36.715
Kim, iti moram.

00:31:37.508 --> 00:31:38.884
Takoj.

00:31:44.917 --> 00:31:46.517
Jebenti.

00:32:17.536 --> 00:32:19.371
Stari, poglej tole.

00:32:21.415 --> 00:32:24.043
