–Ne.

00:32:24.627 --> 00:32:27.546
Colin ali kateri od
sinočnjih bedakov je bil.

00:32:27.796 --> 00:32:29.506
Ne, slišal sem.

00:32:29.798 --> 00:32:32.718
Po žuru sem slišal,
kako nekaj zunaj praska.

00:32:32.968 --> 00:32:34.887
Kako to misliš,
da si slišal nekaj?

00:32:44.605 --> 00:32:46.065
Dobro jutro.

00:32:47.274 --> 00:32:51.278
Poglej se.
Čista in čudovita.

00:32:56.950 --> 00:32:59.036
Lepo.

00:33:04.541 --> 00:33:06.251
Kaj je bilo to?

00:33:10.631 --> 00:33:13.175
John, si odpeljal Kim domov?
–Ja.

00:33:13.801 --> 00:33:15.636
Zdaj pa jo moram sprati s sebe.

00:33:16.178 --> 00:33:17.679
Punca je odvratna!

00:33:18.347 --> 00:33:19.681
Prava prasica.

00:33:19.848 --> 00:33:21.767
Ne govori tega,
to ni kul.

00:33:21.934 --> 00:33:23.477
Tebi je lahko reči.

00:33:23.685 --> 00:33:25.521
Tvoja punca je popolna.

00:33:33.153 --> 00:33:35.322
O, bog.

00:33:35.531 --> 00:33:37.157
Si v redu?

00:33:37.991 --> 00:33:41.036
Ne vem. Mogoče ne bi smela
igrati bejzbola po mrazu.

00:33:41.286 --> 00:33:44.873
Tako je, če si alkoholik.
–Utihni. Sploh nisem veliko spila.

00:33:45.040 --> 00:33:46.667
Mogoče je to težava.

00:33:46.875 --> 00:33:48.460
Skuhal ti bom čaj.

00:34:07.312 --> 00:34:08.730
Pridi.

00:34:11.358 --> 00:34:13.026
Pozabi nanj.

00:34:33.881 --> 00:34:36.884
Medvedek, si se za hip izgubila?

00:34:37.259 --> 00:34:38.844
Sem se?

00:34:41.346 --> 00:34:43.265
Kje si bila?

00:34:45.893 --> 00:34:47.978
Ojoj, treseš se.

00:34:50.397 --> 00:34:52.566
Samo razmišljala sem.

00:34:54.276 --> 00:34:56.111
O Johnu?

00:35:35.901 --> 00:35:39.279
<i>Ne, bratec, v redu je. Veš,
da me lahko kadar koli pokličeš.</i>

00:35:39.863 --> 00:35:42.324
Si res preveč obremenjen?

00:35:42.574 --> 00:35:44.284
Te skrbi,
da moraš paziti name?

00:35:44.534 --> 00:35:45.994
<i>Kaj se dogaja?</i>

00:35:46.286 --> 00:35:47.788
Gre za Sasho?

00:35:48.288 --> 00:35:51.166
Ja, bolna je in prestrašena.

00:35:52.042 --> 00:35:54.044
In John se čudno vede.

00:35:54.461 --> 00:35:56.380
Zdelo se je,
da se imate odlično.

00:35:56.963 --> 00:35:58.423
Res?

00:35:59.049 --> 00:36:00.967
Videl si ju plesati.

00:36:01.635 --> 00:36:03.804
Prijateljček, povej,
kaj se dogaja.

00:36:08.266 --> 00:36:09.601
<i>Elliot?</i>

00:36:12.354 --> 00:36:13.730
Kaj?

00:36:13.980 --> 00:36:17.067
Greva jutri na kosilo,
da se pomeniva?

00:36:17.484 --> 00:36:19.486
Nehati moram.

00:36:19.945 --> 00:36:21.530
Nekaj moram …

00:36:21.780 --> 00:36:23.407
Nekaj moram rešiti.

00:36:24.324 --> 00:36:25.659
El?

00:36:31.748 --> 00:36:33.250
Družba!

00:36:37.587 --> 00:36:39.589
Kaj počneta tam zgoraj?

00:37:45.379 --> 00:37:48.822
