–Preganjavico imaš, stari!

00:40:02.420 --> 00:40:04.296
Ja, vroča si.

00:40:06.215 --> 00:40:08.467
Torej nisi bila z Johnom?

00:40:09.176 --> 00:40:11.011
Imam prisluhe?

00:40:11.429 --> 00:40:13.347
Imam privide?

00:40:16.892 --> 00:40:20.563
Nocoj si mislil, da je hiša prazna,
